text: Emilia Galińska (born 26 December 1992) is a Polish handball player for MKS Zagłębie Lubin and the Polish national team.EHF profile She participated at the 2016 European Women's Handball Championship.2016 European Championship roster ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female handball players Category:People from Łuków County
